OL,5, People could save thousands of pounds  
OL,6, by opting to buy more energy efficient 
OL,7, kitchen appliances, research suggests. 
OL,9,FSignificant savings can be made over   
OL,10,Fthe lifetime of a machine - even with  
OL,11,Fthose that are initially dearer to buy,
OL,12,Fthe consumer group, Which?, said.      
OL,14,FOne #260 tumble dryer cost #135 a year 
OL,15,Fto run - while a more efficient #800   
OL,16,Fdryer cost just #29 a year.            
OL,18,FBut charities criticised a "poverty    
OL,19,Fpremium" preventing those on low       
OL,20,Fincomes from making efficiency savings.
